      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUKEBOX DUKE (5) shapes nicely here coming off a flying 22.53 success at Gawler over 400m. Has the ability and expected to go close again. BLUE PRIDE (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish a neck away in second (17.32) behind MY MUM'S VALUE at this track. Deserves a win and gets his chance. BITTER FURY (4) had a tricky draw last time when running fourth (17.64) over 300m at this track in a Invitation. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Bold showing expected. JADE PALMS (8) was in the money last start despite a big quote and is likely to feature again.",
